DOC.brief_summary: The Prenatal Nutrition Psychosocial Health Outcomes ( PreNAPS ) study two year collaboration Gulu , Makarere , Cornell , Tufts Universities . The PreNAPs study 's primary goal : ) determine differential impact food insecurity gestational weight gain prenatal depression , b ) elucidate mechanism underlie relationship food insecurity weight gain and/depression among HIV infect HIV uninfected pregnant woman Gulu , Northern Uganda .
